      "para_id": "Q000963.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanše , the mighty lady , lady of the boundaries , his lady , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built the E-šeššeše-ĝara , her beloved temple ."
